                                    <locus from="4v" to="76v" scheme="folios"/>
                                    <note>Additions in the margin in brown ink by a contemporary hand (perhaps by the scribe). Some of these glosses may be part of the planned layout. Glosses usually just one word, but sometimes a short phrase and on <locus from="51v" to="51v" scheme="folios"/> a longer addition with signe-de-renvoi.</note>
